text: Tamás Sudár (born 13 July 1941) is a Hungarian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Hungary Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
